data.description: Welcome to 29 Nicole Court! Nestled on a cul-de-sac road in desired neighborhood, this contemporary home boasts 5-6 bedrooms, 3 1/2 bathrooms, and a bonus flex space in the lower level. Step inside and be greeted by a spacious living room, dining room, and eat-in Kitchen. Down the hall is a full bath, room that could be anything you need - bedroom, office, den, or playroom alike, tandem with another bedroom. Rest assured that this home & pool are equipped with newer mechanicals and components as well as a new garage door. The added bonus of solar panels allows for reduced electric expenses, making this property both eco-friendly and cost-effective. Outside, you'll discover an in-ground pool, offering the perfect space to relax and entertain during the hot summers. Don't miss the opportunity to make this East Haven gem your own. With its abundance of space, natural light, and enticing features, this contemporary home is ready to welcome you into a world of endless possibilities.
